# ── TaoStats API ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Obtain a key at: https://dash.taostats.io
#
# With this key set:
#   • /api/subnets returns the full live ~128-subnet list from TaoStats
#   • The subnet explorer upgrades from the 12-subnet static snapshot to
#     the complete network on first page load (no restart required)
#   • npm run fetch-subnets regenerates lib/data/subnets-real.ts with
#     live metrics baked in (useful for zero-JS / static deployments)
#
# Without this key:
#   • The app runs normally using the curated 12-subnet static snapshot
#   • /api/subnets returns X-Data-Source: static-snapshot
#
# IMPORTANT: Never use NEXT_PUBLIC_TAOSTATS_API_KEY — that would expose
# the key in the browser bundle. This variable is server-side only.
#
TAOSTATS_API_KEY=your_taostats_api_key_here

# ── Dev stability note ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# If the dev server shows stale styles or broken hot-reload after pulling
# new changes, run:
#
#   npm run clean && npm run dev
#
# This clears the .next build cache. Root cause: Next.js sometimes fails to
# detect that Tailwind-generated CSS classes have changed across branches.
